{"word":"G3908 - παρατίθημι - paratíthēmi - par-at-ith'-ay-mee - Allege","slug":"G3908","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">παρατίθημι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>paratíthēmi"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>par-at-ith'-ay-mee"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Allege"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03C0;&#x03B1;&#x03C1;&#x03B1;&#x03C4;&#x03B9;&#x0301;&#x03B8;&#x03B7;&#x03BC;&#x03B9; - paratithe&#x0304;mi</b> - <i>par-at-ith'-ay-mee</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G3844\">G3844</a> and <a href=\"#/G5087\">G5087</a>; to <i>place alongside</i>, that is, <i>present</i> (food, truth); by implication to <i>deposit</i> (as a trust or for protection): - allege, commend, commit (the keeping of), put forth, set before."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G114\">G114</a>, <a href=\"#/G115\">G115</a>, <a href=\"#/G1936\">G1936</a>, <a href=\"#/G2007\">G2007</a>, <a href=\"#/G3331\">G3331</a>, <a href=\"#/G3346\">G3346</a>, <a href=\"#/G3866\">G3866</a>, <a href=\"#/G4286\">G4286</a>, <a href=\"#/G4369\">G4369</a>, <a href=\"#/G4388\">G4388</a>, <a href=\"#/G5087\">G5087</a>"}]}